      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "1f869566301c9e0f",
      "text": "The advantage I see for this is the separation of responsibility between federated platform developers and platform as a service providers. The challenge/opportunity is to construct a reliable web of trust so as to prevent or recover from abuse."
